  • Packages that use TO 
    Package Description
    com.franza.Academic.ac
    This package stores the application controller classes that implement the correspondent abstract class.
    com.franza.Academic.beans
    This package stores the interfaces (generic, local and remote) and the java beans classes that implement the former ones.
    com.franza.Academic.model
    Package that stores the entity bean classes that implement the correspondent abstract class.
    com.franza.Academic.to
    Package that stores the transfer object classes that implement the correspondent interface methods.
